##### Password Reset
**Username:** {username}
**System:** {system}

A temporary password has been generated and sent to the user's registered email address.
The user will be prompted to create a new password upon first login.

##### Software Installation
**Software:** {software_name}
**Version:** {version}
**System:** {system}

The software has been queued for installation on the specified system.
Installation will complete within 30 minutes and the user will be notified.

##### Support Ticket Created
**User:** {user}
**Issue:** {issue}
**Priority:** {priority}
