A support ticket has been created and assigned to the appropriate team.
The user will receive updates via email as the ticket is processed.

##### User Added to Group
**Username:** {username}
**Group:** {group_name}

The user has been successfully added to the specified group.
Access changes will take effect within 15 minutes.

##### System Update
**System:** {system}
**Update Type:** {update_type}

The system update has been scheduled for the next maintenance window.
Users will be notified in advance of any potential downtime.

##### Security Scan
**System:** {system}
**Scan Type:** {scan_type}

The security scan has been initiated and will run in the background.
Results will be available in the security dashboard once completed.
